ISLAMABAD, Aug 08 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting, Senator Shibli Faraz on Saturday said the Ravi River project was the foundation of a Naya Lahore in the Naya Pakistan, which would pave way for investment and provide vast employment opportunities to people.
In a tweet, he said plantation, lake and water treatment plant projects would make Lahore beautiful and environment friendly city.
